            "annotation_id": "MI_111"
        },
        {
            "decision": "If the drain is connected to a collection container, please note color, consistency, and amount of fluid in the drain. Call the doctor, nurse practitioner, or VNA nurse if the amount increases significantly or changes in character. Be sure to empty the drain frequently. Record the output, if instructed to do so.",
